Legitimate Interest:
We rely on legitimate interest in connection with our processing of data for security purposes such as, authentication, identity verification and fraud and spam prevention. This may include URLs included in messages and messages, which were reported as SPAM by other users, or were otherwise suspected to be unsolicited and using your operating system authentication services. We may use automated decisions to close or restrict an account based on such data and other logic we have created for this, in order to protect other users and prevent recurring breaches.
