Changes to This CCPA Notice
This notice was last updated on January 1, 2025. We may revise or update this CCPA Notice from time to time, and in any event, as required under the CCPA, we will
update
the CCPA Notice
every 12 months
. If changes to this privacy notice will have a fundamental impact on the nature of the processing or otherwise have a substantial impact on you, we will give you sufficient advance notice so that you have the opportunity to exercise your rights (e.g. to object to the processing).
The last revision date will be reflected in the “Last Modified” heading at the top of this CCPA Notice.
